Paste JSON below, upload a JSON file, or drag & drop.
After pasting, uploading, or dropping a file, the simple textarea is filled with the JSON content, ready to be submitted.
While dragging a file over the page, a dotted border and helper text in the target both appear. When the mouse cursor hovers over the target, the target becomes shaded.
Clicking the link activates the system file selector dialog, filtered to JSON by default, using <input accept=".json" type="file"> behind the scenes.
